@startuml folio-copyeditor-use-cases
' Folio — Copyeditor essentials (copyedit.view_queue, copyedit.submit_note, copyedit.publish)
' Excludes editor assign-copyeditor and author "mark ready" flows
' Render: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle stickman

actor "Copyeditor" as CE

rectangle "Folio — copyeditor scope" {

  usecase "Handle copyedit assignment" as UC_Handle
  usecase "Browse copyedit queue" as UC_List
  usecase "Send copyedit queries to author" as UC_Queries
  usecase "Publish submission to catalog" as UC_Publish
}

CE --> UC_Handle

UC_Handle .> UC_List : <<include>>
UC_Handle .> UC_Queries : <<include>>
UC_Publish .> UC_Handle : <<extend>>

note bottom of UC_Queries
  Notes for author (and optional
  confidential note to editor).
  Author uploads a revised manuscript
  and marks ready before publish.
end note

note bottom of UC_Publish
  When assignment is ready_for_review
  and submission is in copyediting;
  all copyedit assignments on the
  submission must be ready.
end note

note right of UC_Handle
  Editors **assign** copyeditors;
  journal managers grant the role.
  Author **mark ready** is on the
  author workflow.
end note

@enduml
